{"type":"message","id":"ba2bc821","parentId":"ce65f0f1","timestamp":"2026-05-25T01:17:58.393Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6e0e7ac358acc3326f4fb5e1157\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-05-25 09:17 GMT+8\",\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\nReply target of current user message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"body\": \"[message_id=om_x100b6e0db537a8a4b3c76b837bc48fc] ⚠️ Cron job \\\"TK选品每日9AM推送\\\" failed: FailoverError: The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment.\"\n}\n```\n\n这意思是推送失败了，还是选品失败了"}],"timestamp":1779671878261}}
{"type":"message","id":"b3a706af","parentId":"ba2bc821","timestamp":"2026-05-25T01:18:05.769Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about a cron job failure message. They're wondering if the push failed or the product selection failed.\n\nThe error says \"⚠️ Cron job \"TK选品每日9AM推送\" failed: FailoverError: The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment.\"\n\nThis error message says \"AI service is temporarily overloaded\" - this is an infrastructure/service issue, not a product selection logic failure. It's saying the AI service (the LLM API) was overloaded when trying to run the selection job.\n\nSo it's a **推送失败** (push failure) caused by the AI service being overloaded, not a **选品失败** (product selection failure) in terms of the logic/algorithm.\n","thinkingSignature":"b68439e5e26d281b75909c2a558c4e27382e4d9b8379f5d4c4264e0b8db8ffaf"},{"type":"text","text":"是**推送失败**，但原因不是选品逻辑的问题——是 AI 服务（LLM API）临时过载了。\n\n简单说就是：cron 任务按时触发了，但在执行过程中调用 AI 接口时被告知\"服务器忙，稍后再试\"，所以整个任务失败了。这不是选品数据或 SOP 逻辑的问题，就是调用 OpenAI/Minimax 这类 AI 服务时遇到的暂时性负载问题。\n\n一般来说重跑一次大概率就过了。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":270,"output":242,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":45461,"totalTokens":45973,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779671878674,"responseId":"0662d647f68e6c8cb3fce3ff6284fa65"}}
